{"tid":1947100,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"車中泊","createTime":"2020-03-28T05:17:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T13:07:53.000Z","uid":2247,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"262ac605dc2c0cfa8bc0f03f60e07557306e3a6e","tid":1947100,"uid":2247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T05:17:17.000Z","msg":"話說一直以黎都有睇開日本仔車中泊既片<br />\n但一直以黎都覺得呢個概念要係香港實行好On9 始終空地唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴打試過？個感覺係咪好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n架仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dgyp43L69ck\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fdgyp43L69ck&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOqxnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=4465b355\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dgyp43L69ck</a><br />\n<br />\n本地<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yE2R5bGDhdY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyE2R5bGDhdY&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOqxnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=3b44eabf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yE2R5bGDhdY</a>"},{"pid":"1f3dbeeb8f7338711543b068dca2027904b75d51","tid":1947100,"uid":51041,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T05:30:37.000Z","msg":"香港玩始終太多限制<br />\n<br />\n地方細<br />\n樣樣貴<br />\n<br />\n法例又落後<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f06e6e891ed1a6061442b375db06a54ef00d853","tid":1947100,"uid":2247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T05:34:40.000Z","msg":"灰鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99601b5cdcdd44b4d3b77ecb4512e842480acda4","tid":1947100,"uid":18177,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T05:36:28.000Z","msg":"香港咁細泊喺邊度？<br />\n<br />\n人哋日本泊車地方附近又有景又小人，香港真係全程屈喺架車度，一出車就周圍都係人，<br />\n<br />\n仲要免費俾其他人參觀，冇哂私隱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05a42572a4140b0c31c18fb8e651c0ce4e804f13","tid":1947100,"uid":58736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T10:43:32.000Z","msg":"車中泊 香港真係唔襟玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24bff9cf71ef721c58d3d1de492d951965cb9be8","tid":1947100,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T10:46:20.000Z","msg":"仲慘過住劏房"},{"pid":"853cedfd9ee5923da1083a7b6a5900fd9abf3e80","tid":1947100,"uid":37751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:29:59.000Z","msg":"就改裝呢一點 已經煩啦"},{"pid":"9ba039d9a16050a9a4003ca13fd974580c097365","tid":1947100,"uid":4032,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:05:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCaXvf3nm0Th672r5gUcTomA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCaXvf3nm0Th672r5gUcTomA%2F&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOqxnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=1587f6fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCaXvf3nm0Th672r5gUcTomA/</a><br />\nテルさんTV <br />\n<br />\n呢個 Channel 個車中泊（多數都係過一晚）拍得好靚，尤其啲嘢食。<br />\n見佢好似無咩改裝。可以參考下。"},{"pid":"fdd6866a67bcf277f7063e402c01505e9c4f8008","tid":1947100,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:15:45.000Z","msg":"香港最大問題係19法例<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果係車位，會話你違反土地用途，車位唔可以住人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果唔係車位，就會話你違例泊車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要啲冇車位而唔係違例泊車 e.g. offroad/ 200米冇街燈嘅位先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"927352765c80fac530f4cf54e0a498eb725f535b","tid":1947100,"uid":2247,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyT