I.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果唔係車位，就會話你違例泊車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要啲冇車位而唔係違例泊車 e.g. offroad/ 200米冇街燈嘅位先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:40:02.000Z","msg":"改裝少少又犯法"},{"pid":"547aef21c12e8971b1e2a8b77b64602a04fdce1a","tid":1947100,"uid":33655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:47:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yofU9b6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyofU9b6.png&h=2ece1d0c&s={SIZE}\" />呢個channel都唔錯"},{"pid":"e55f4bbe012c81d42361919440a9f05c72540f59","tid":1947100,"uid":107927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T13:07:53.000Z","msg":"要有能力自己改裝，驗車果陣又要拆晒d改裝，覺得太煩，要好有愛先會玩。<br />\n一般人寧願揸架車去露營就算，仲舒服過瞓係車掛。我見佢都係推介郊野公園campsite，咁直接露營就得啦。當然可能有其他私家正位廢事公開驚多人去。"}]}